org.yamcs.ui.eventviewer

Class FilteringRulesTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • org.yamcs.ui.eventviewer.FilteringRulesTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, TableModel

    public class FilteringRulesTable
extends AbstractTableModel
    Table with filtering rules. The rules are matched from top to bottom, there is always default rule. If none of the rules does apply for the event, then the default rule is used. All rules are stored in the Preferences backing store.
